    "---Background Information --system manages the task as a Directed Acyclic Graph (DAG).",
    "In this turn, you need to decompose the tasks and arrange them in chronological order.",
    "Next turn we will analyse your result json to a graph.",
    "A subtask-structure has the following json component: { \"id\": int, id of the subtask start from 1, \"action\": string, name of the action, \"required subtasks\": list[int], if this subtask is directly prerequisite for other subtasks before it, list the subtask id here.",
    "\"assigned_agent\": str, name of agent."
  ],
